description: Title displayed on feed page when there are no fact-checks to be listed.
Message displayed on feed page when there are no fact-checks to be listed. English values for placeholders link text: 'resetLink' is 'resetting filters' and 'listLink' is 'source list'.
defaultMessage: Try {resetLink} to find fact-checks or verify that the {listLink} has items

description: Link text that is part of message displayed when a feed does not return any fact-checks. The message where it appears reads: 'Try resetting filters to find fact-checks'.

Text that is part of message displayed when a feed does not return any fact-checks.
